{
  "$comment": "daodao AI pipeline 單一事實來源（SSOT）。所有腳本、skill、文件引用此檔，不得另行硬編碼。修改此檔需 PR review。",
  "version": 3,
  "org": "daodaoedu",
  "monorepo": "daodao",
  "workRoot": "/tmp/daodao-work",
  "highRiskRepos": [
    "daodao-storage",
    "daodao-infra"
  ],
  "repos": {
    "daodao-server": {
      "defaultBranch": "dev",
      "install": "pnpm install --frozen-lockfile",
      "quality": {
        "fix": "pnpm run lint:fix",
        "lint": "pnpm run lint",
        "typecheck": "pnpm run typecheck",
        "test": "pnpm test"
      },
      "formatFile": "npx eslint --fix \"{file}\"",
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：null/undefined 處理、async/await、錯誤處理路徑",
        "安全：SQL injection、缺少認證/授權、輸入驗證（Zod）",
        "效能：不必要的資料庫查詢、大量資料未分頁、缺少 cache",
        "架構：service 層分離、禁用 any、factory 函式而非 class、API response 格式一致"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-f2e": {
      "defaultBranch": "dev",
      "install": "pnpm install --frozen-lockfile",
      "quality": {
        "fix": "pnpm run check:fix",
        "lint": "pnpm run lint",
        "typecheck": "pnpm run typecheck",
        "test": "pnpm test"
      },
      "formatFile": "npx biome check --write \"{file}\"",
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：條件判斷、邊界情況、錯誤處理",
        "安全：XSS、注入攻擊、敏感資料外洩",
        "效能：不必要的 re-render、N+1 query、缺少 memo/useMemo",
        "架構：使用 @daodao/* packages、元件拆分合理性"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-ai-backend": {
      "defaultBranch": "dev",
      "install": "uv sync",
      "quality": {
        "fix": "make format",
        "lint": "make check && make lint",
        "typecheck": null,
        "test": "make test"
      },
      "formatFile": "uv run black \"{file}\" && uv run ruff check --fix \"{file}\"",
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：async 處理、異常路徑、None 處理",
        "安全：SQL injection、缺少認證、prompt injection 面",
        "效能：資料庫查詢、大量資料未分頁、缺少 cache",
        "架構：FastAPI 模式、service 層分離"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-admin-ui": {
      "defaultBranch": "dev",
      "install": "pnpm install --frozen-lockfile",
      "quality": {
        "fix": "pnpm run check:fix",
        "lint": "pnpm run lint",
        "typecheck": "npx tsc --noEmit",
        "test": "pnpm run test"
      },
      "formatFile": "npx biome check --write \"{file}\"",
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：條件判斷、邊界情況、錯誤處理",
        "安全：XSS、注入攻擊、敏感資料外洩",
        "效能：不必要的 re-render、缺少 memo/useMemo",
        "架構：單一 axios instance（不用 fetch）、shadcn/ui 元件慣例"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-worker": {
      "defaultBranch": "main",
      "install": "npm install",
      "quality": {
        "fix": null,
        "lint": null,
        "typecheck": "npm run typecheck",
        "test": "npm test"
      },
      "formatFile": null,
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：條件判斷、邊界情況、錯誤處理",
        "安全：CORS 設定、secrets 使用",
        "效能：不必要的 KV/R2 呼叫、cold start、bundle size",
        "架構：Hono 路由結構、Cloudflare Workers 限制"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-mcp": {
      "defaultBranch": "main",
      "install": "pnpm install --frozen-lockfile",
      "quality": {
        "fix": null,
        "lint": null,
        "typecheck": "pnpm run typecheck",
        "test": "pnpm run test"
      },
      "formatFile": null,
      "reviewFocus": [
        "邏輯錯誤：條件判斷、邊界情況、錯誤處理",
        "MCP 協定正確性：tool schema、錯誤回傳格式"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-storage": {
      "defaultBranch": "main",
      "install": null,
      "quality": {
        "fix": null,
        "lint": null,
        "typecheck": null,
        "test": null
      },
      "formatFile": null,
      "reviewFocus": [
        "migration 不可變性：已套用的 migration 禁止修改",
        "schema 相容性：破壞性變更需要 migration 計畫"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    },
    "daodao-infra": {
      "defaultBranch": "main",
      "install": null,
      "quality": {
        "fix": null,
        "lint": null,
        "typecheck": null,
        "test": null
      },
      "formatFile": null,
      "reviewFocus": [
        "IaC 安全：secrets 不入版控、最小權限",
        "部署風險：不可逆操作需人工確認"
      ],
      "protectedPaths": [
        ".github/workflows/*",
        ".env*",
        "secrets/*",
        "migrate/sql/*"
      ]
    }
  },
  "models": {
    "$comment": "供 code-review 第三引擎與未來 council 使用。session 模型由 CCR routine 設定決定，不在此控制。",
    "dispatch": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
    "reviewer": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
    "judge": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001"
  },
  "scopeCaps": {
    "$comment": "token cap 在 v3 移除（無法在 session-native 模式下量測），改用可強制執行的 proxy：檔案數與 diff 行數。verify.sh 強制檢查。",
    "XS": {
      "maxFiles": 3,
      "maxDiffLines": 300
    },
    "S": {
      "maxFiles": 10,
      "maxDiffLines": 1200
    },
    "M": {
      "maxFiles": 30,
      "maxDiffLines": 4000
    },
    "L": {
      "maxFiles": 0,
      "maxDiffLines": 0
    }
  },
  "quotas": {
    "fetchPerRepo": 10,
    "operatePerRound": 5,
    "prPatrolPerRound": 3,
    "verifyAttempts": 2
  }
}
